Necro -- Summoner, starting stats 6 int, 0 agi, 4 str, base speed 290, base damage 3, Stats Gain per level 1.30 int, 1.00 str, 0.00 agi
starting item Skeletal Wand increase intelligence by 2 and give 1.5 mana regen base attack time 1.65

LEVEL 20 TALENT

talent 1

give 6.5 life-regen, 250 life and 25% magic resist

talent 2

give 9 mana regen, 15 int and 200 cast range



PASSIVE CORE D OR F
Corrupted Flesh
increase all stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF Necro has 15% base magic resist at start and his skeleton regen 1% of their life per second he also gain 3% movement speed per
skeleton alive and for every 5 level Necro gain 1% magic resist he also gain 50% of his strenght as inteillgence bonus and he start
with a special Chest Peice item that can be change
DEBUFF Necro will take 80% more damage from physical and he doesnt gain any agility per level he also need 16 int to gain 1% spell amp
and strenght only gain 4 life instead of 5 and he also need 10 inteillgence to gain 1 damage instead of 5 inteillgence

Bone Armor Special item
increase armor by 2
increase armor by 10%
reduce pure damage by 12%
can also be use to give this bonus to skeleton only for 50% of the bonus

talent level 25, upgrade Corrupted Flesh
give a new modfier Death Walks Among Us
any enemy that die near Necro 900 radius will be reanimated as a skeleton
that last for 25 second with 100% of the normal Skeleton Warrior stats as well they got 6% chance to have 200% instead


SPELL Q
Skeleton Warrior
Summon a Skeleton Warrior to fight for you, they are really weak to area of effect and can die very fast to high damage they also
have a chance to deal more damage and lifestealing and attacking faster

Skeleton life 25 40 75 100 plus 65% of int
Skeleton damage 3-4 4-5 5-6 6-7 plus 6% of int
Skeleton armor 1, every 40 int it will give the skeleton 1 armor
Skeleton magic resist 5% plus 5% 6% 7% 8% of int
Skeleton base attack time 2.3 2.2 2.1 2.0
Max skeleton 3 5 7 9
Mana cost 100 120 140 160 plus 3% of max mana
cooldown 1

Skeleton passive
Swing of the dead
they get 12% chance to deal 140% damage after that they get 4 instance of 20% lifesteal and 15 attack speed, the final
hit will deal 10 pure damage plus 25% of the skeleton damage into pure, cooldown 3 second

talent level 10 upgrade Skeleton warrior

Skeleton life Increase by 30
Skeleton damage increase by 1-3
Skeleton armor increase by 1
Skeleton magic resist increase by 5%
Skeleton base attack time reduce by 0.40
Max skeleton increase by 6

add a new modifier Bone Wave
every time the Skeleton warrior attack they will make a Bone Wave in front of them that travel only 350 far and 200 radius
that deal 70% of the skeleton damage to the enemys and those enemys hit by the Bone Wave will have 10% chance to be rooted for 0.3 second
and after the root end it will damage them by 0.3% of their max health 0.1% current life for bosses

SPELL W
Skeleton Archer
Summon Skeleton Archer To fight against your foes, those skeleton will come with a element that will help and deal
great damage to the enemy

Skeleton Archer life 16 24 32 40 plus 40% of int
Skeleton Archer damage 5-10 6-12 7-14 8-16 plus 12% of int
Skeleton Archer armor 0, every 60 int will give the skeleton archer 1 armor
Skeleton Archer magic resist 0% plus 10% of int
Skeleton Archer base attack time 2.3 2.1 1.9 1.7
Max skeleton archer 1 2 3 4
mana cost 150 190 230 270 plus 3% of max mana
cooldown 1

Skeleton Archer passive 1 OF EACH MAX
Elemental being

POISON ARCHER
every attack poison the target dealing 2 4 6 8 pure damage per second plus 5% of the Skeleton Archer damage and reducing healing effect
by 10% and last 3 second, also 50% 55% 60% 65% of the poison archer damage is Pure

ICE ARCHER
every attack Slow the target movementspeed by 6% 7% 8% 9% and attackspeed by 4 6 8 10 also dealing 3 6 9 12 physical damage per second
plus 10% of the Skeleton Archer damage last 3 second

FIRE ARCHER
the fire archer has 14% 16% 18% 20% chance to deal 140% 160% 180% 200%, melting the armor and reducing it by 1 2 3 4 last 6 second

LIGHTNING ARCHER
deal 4 5 6 7 magical damage per attack plus 30% of the archer damage as well and reducing magic resist by 2% 6% 10% 14% last 2.5 second

talent level 10 upgrade Skeleton archer

base attack time reduce by 0.30
max skeleton archer increase by 2
POISON ARCHER damage per second increase by 2
ICE ARCHER movementspeed slow increase by 8%
FIRE ARCHER armor reduction increase by 3
LIGHTNING ARCHER magic resist reduction increase by 11%

add 2 new skeleton archer

VOID ARCHER
the void archer has 9% 10% 11% 12% to stun for 0.4 second and dealing 15 25 35 45 physical damage plus 10% of the
archer damage and silencing them for 1.2 second after the stun

DARK ARCHER
the dark archer has 15% 20% 25% 30% to blind the target and causing them to miss for 13% 17% 21% 25% last 3 second
also making the dark archer get 15 25 35 45 attack speed for 1.5 1.7 1.9 2.1 second

 
SPELL E
Death Coil
heal ally skeleton or damage enemy, also reduce the enemy regen and increase skeleton damage and attack speed

damage 10 20 30 40 magical plus 50% of int
heal 20 40 60 80 can only affect skeleton of necro
bonus heal 8% 12% 16% 20% of max health
enemy regen reduction -4 -7 -10 -13 last 4 second
skeleton increase damage 4 8 12 16 last 6 second
skeleton attack speed increase 7 14 21 28 last 6 second
mana cost 150 plus 2% 3% 4% 5% of max mana
cooldown 14


talent level 15 upgrade Death Coil
increase the damage of Death Coil by 5
increase int scaling by 20%
increase heal by 40
increase bonus heal by 7%
increase enemy regen reduction by -9
skeleton damage increase by 8
skeleton attack speed increase by 12

add a new modifier Bouncing Coil
now the death coil will bounce 7 time each bounce will deal 10% more damage and heal per bounce
if cast on enemy it will only try to bounce on enemy if there is no enemy left it will start bouncing on skeleton
if cast on skeletons it will only try to bounce on skeletons if there is no skeleton left it will start bouncing on enemy
if any enemys die by Death Coil it will Summon a new one for only 50% of the damage and still get increase damage per bounce


