ULTIMATE R
Death Touch
casting Death Touch on any Summon will give it to all of them increasing damage,attack speed,armor and magic resist or if casted on 
enemys they will suffer insane damage per second losing magic resist,attack speed and reducing all type of damage they do

IF CAST ON ENEMY
damage per second 25 50 75 plus 30% 40% 50% of int -damage type magical-
enemy magic resist lost 10% 18% 26%
enemy attack speed lost 25 35 45
enemy damage reduction 20% 30% 40%
duration 6

IF CASTED ON SKELETON
bonus base damage 11 22 33
bonus attack speed 25 40 55
bonus armor 3 7 11
bonus magic resist 20% 40% 60%
last 10 11 12 second

mana cost 150 plus 30% of max mana
cooldown 95 90 85

talent level 25 upgrade Death Touch
increase damage by 10
increase int scaling by 30%
increase magic resist lost by 10%
increase damage lost by 5%
increase bonus damage by 11
increase attack speed bonus 10

add a new modifier Bless by the Death God
Enemys that die under Death Touch will Spread it to other target for 80% of the damage and for 4 second duration, Necro also get Heal by
35% of the damage dealt by Death Touch. Death Touch can also be cast on allys for 50% of its bonus with 25% more duration on them
and for Skeleton every time they kill something under Death Touch, they will gain 1% life bonus up to 40% and it will last until they die
